1. To be more precise, in pre-consumer societies where transactions were largely unwritten, litigation occured as a way of establishing the terms of transactions.

- To be more precise : 보다 정확히 말해
- in pre-consumer societies: 소비자 이전 사회에서
- where transactions were largerly unwritten,: 거래가 대개 기록되지 않은 곳
- litigation occured as a way of establishing the terms of transactions: 소송은 거래의 조건을 설립하는 역할을 했다.

- words
precise: 정확한
pre-consumer societies: 소비자 이전 사회
transactions: 거래
largely: 대개
unwritten: 기록되지 않은
term: 조건, 용어
occured as: 방식으로 발생했다, 수단으로 작용했다

litigation, suit: 소송, 기소
coalition: 연합, 제휴
tariff: 관세
quandary: 진퇴양난

- point:
litigation occured as a way of establishing the terms of transactions

2. During her two terms in office, Stein has become a symbol of innovation and fired up young conservatives who are fed up with politicians with provincial, outdated views.

- During her two terms in office, :  그녀의 사무실에서의 두 번의 임기 동안에,
- Stein has become a symbol of innovation: Stein은 혁신의 상징이 되었고
- and fired up young conservatives who are fed up with politicians with provincial, outdated views.: 편협하고 구식의 시각을 가진 정치인들에게 신물이 난 젊은 보수주의자들에게 열의를 불어넣었다.

- words
term: (재임)기간, 임기
fire up(has fired up): 열의[흥미]를 불어넣다
conservative: 보수주의자
provincial: 편협한, 옹졸한, 지방의, 지역적인

be fed with, be disgusted at: 신물이 난, 진저리치는
enamored of: 현혹된, 매혹된
dubious of: 의심하는
alienatedfrom: 소외된

- point

3. Senefelder wrote his laundry list on a limestone plate with crayon made of wax, soap, and a black pigment. Afterwards, he placed the limestone in acid and discovered that the laundry list he had written with the crayon appeared in relief.

- Senefelder wrote his laundry list on a limestone plate with crayon made of wax, soap, and a black pigment.: Senefelder는 그의 빨래 목록을 석회암에 왁스, 비누, 검은 연료로 만든 크레용으로 적었다.
- Afterwards, he placed the limestone in acid and discovered that the laundry list he had written with the crayon appeared in relief.: 그 다음, 그는 산성 물질에 석회암을 놓고 그가 크레용으로 적은 빨래 목록아 양각으로 드러나는 것을 발견했다.
